1
00:00:10,625 --> 00:00:13,666
[wind gusting]

2
00:00:17,750 --> 00:00:19,958
[groaning softly]

3
00:00:34,458 --> 00:00:36,666
[wind blowing harder]

4
00:00:45,625 --> 00:00:46,916
[FUBUKI]
Yumi.

5
00:00:47,000 --> 00:00:48,333
Let's end this.

6
00:00:50,541 --> 00:00:52,000
[BOTH grunt]

7
00:01:01,708 --> 00:01:03,333
Asuka.

8
00:01:03,416 --> 00:01:05,416
[groaning]

9
00:01:12,208 --> 00:01:14,250
We'll never let you hurt Asuka!

10
00:01:14,333 --> 00:01:17,625
♪

11
00:01:17,708 --> 00:01:20,875
It doesn't matter how many
of you there might be,

12
00:01:20,958 --> 00:01:23,666
I will eliminate
every single shinobi.

13
00:01:23,750 --> 00:01:25,000
For Fubuki's sake.

14
00:01:25,083 --> 00:01:27,458
Even if it costs me my own life!

15
00:01:28,541 --> 00:01:29,916
[ASUKA]
Hey.

16
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:31,500
-At least tell me one thing.
-[KATSURAGI] Asuka.

17
00:01:31,583 --> 00:01:34,291
Why are you willing to risk
everything for Fubuki?

18
00:01:35,833 --> 00:01:39,291
If you must know, it's because
her mother once saved my life.

19
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:43,875
You find that bizarre,
don't you?

20
00:01:43,958 --> 00:01:45,541
That I would be willing
to face death

21
00:01:45,625 --> 00:01:47,041
in order to repay an old debt?

22
00:01:48,333 --> 00:01:49,625
No, not at all.

23
00:01:49,708 --> 00:01:51,541
I think it's admirable.

24
00:01:51,625 --> 00:01:53,833
I can see where
you're coming from.

25
00:01:53,916 --> 00:01:55,000
[RASETSU]
But?

26
00:01:55,083 --> 00:01:56,333
But...

27
00:01:56,416 --> 00:01:59,666
I can't allow you
to destroy the shinobi!

28
00:01:59,750 --> 00:02:01,916
[RASETSU]
So, what do you intend to do?

29
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:03,833
Seal me away like the others?

30
00:02:03,916 --> 00:02:05,041
[ASUKA]
Exactly!

31
00:02:05,125 --> 00:02:07,416
Because I'm not afraid
to die, either!

32
00:02:07,500 --> 00:02:08,833
Hey!

33
00:02:10,000 --> 00:02:12,791
♪

34
00:02:16,500 --> 00:02:19,291
So, please. Lend me
your strength, everybody!

35
00:02:19,375 --> 00:02:21,916
[ALL]
Shinobi Transformation!

36
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:25,958
♪

37
00:04:01,125 --> 00:04:03,166
[MINORI] Hey. You sure this is
the right way?

38
00:04:03,250 --> 00:04:06,041
Yes. Last I saw, Yumi was headed
in this direction.

39
00:04:06,125 --> 00:04:07,833
I'm just so worried.

40
00:04:07,916 --> 00:04:09,541
I really hope
that she's all right.

41
00:04:09,625 --> 00:04:12,041
[blades clanging in distance]

42
00:04:12,125 --> 00:04:13,458
Look over there!

43
00:04:14,541 --> 00:04:16,541
[YOZAKURA]
Shinobi Transformation!

44
00:04:17,625 --> 00:04:19,041
[BOTH yell]

45
00:04:19,125 --> 00:04:20,666
[grunting]

46
00:04:24,041 --> 00:04:25,750
[IKARUGA screams]

47
00:04:26,750 --> 00:04:28,000
[ALL grunt]

48
00:04:29,125 --> 00:04:29,958
[grunts]

49
00:04:34,541 --> 00:04:36,541
[yelling]

50
00:04:39,833 --> 00:04:41,375
[grunting]

51
00:04:46,083 --> 00:04:48,791
[groaning]

52
00:04:51,041 --> 00:04:53,833
Now, Asuka! Do it!

53
00:04:53,916 --> 00:04:56,541
Right!
Super Secret Ninja Art!

54
00:04:56,625 --> 00:04:58,875
Fuma Korin!

55
00:05:01,791 --> 00:05:03,583
[screaming]

56
00:05:03,666 --> 00:05:05,625
It's done! [groans]

57
00:05:06,625 --> 00:05:07,791
Finally,

58
00:05:07,875 --> 00:05:09,083
this can all end.

59
00:05:09,166 --> 00:05:12,333
[RASETSU groaning]

60
00:05:12,416 --> 00:05:15,208
Rasetsu, please be careful.

61
00:05:15,291 --> 00:05:18,166
They will undoubtedly attempt
to use Fuma Korin.

62
00:05:18,250 --> 00:05:20,083
Of course,
I am fighting shinobi,

63
00:05:20,166 --> 00:05:21,875
so I'd expect nothing less.

64
00:05:21,958 --> 00:05:25,333
Besides, do you really think
I'll be so easy to seal?

65
00:05:27,416 --> 00:05:28,958
Of course not.

66
00:05:29,041 --> 00:05:31,375
I'll be counting
on your strength until the end.

67
00:05:31,458 --> 00:05:34,083
More power.

68
00:05:34,166 --> 00:05:36,875
I just need a little more power!

69
00:05:36,958 --> 00:05:38,833
That's all I want.

70
00:05:38,916 --> 00:05:40,291
Even if I...

71
00:05:40,375 --> 00:05:41,416
[sobs]

72
00:05:41,500 --> 00:05:44,625
Fubuki, this is goodbye.

73
00:05:44,708 --> 00:05:48,916
[yelling, roaring]

74
00:05:50,833 --> 00:05:52,291
[growling]

75
00:05:52,375 --> 00:05:54,250
-[HOMURA] What the hell?
-No way!

76
00:05:54,333 --> 00:05:57,291
[roaring]

77
00:06:01,375 --> 00:06:02,958
Well, it's about time
you showed us

78
00:06:03,041 --> 00:06:04,333
the monster you really are!

79
00:06:07,833 --> 00:06:08,791
[grunts]

80
00:06:08,875 --> 00:06:10,166
That's crazy!

81
00:06:10,250 --> 00:06:12,000
It could destroy a whole city
in this form!

82
00:06:12,083 --> 00:06:13,458
We have to stop it here!

83
00:06:17,125 --> 00:06:19,875
[ASUKA groaning]

84
00:06:22,125 --> 00:06:24,791
♪

85
00:06:33,041 --> 00:06:35,541
[FUBUKI]
Why am I thinking of that now?

86
00:06:35,625 --> 00:06:39,041
♪

87
00:06:39,125 --> 00:06:41,583
[RASETSU growling]

88
00:06:43,125 --> 00:06:44,583
Just hang in there, Asuka!

89
00:06:44,666 --> 00:06:46,583
Whatever, Homura.

90
00:06:46,666 --> 00:06:48,916
You should be worrying
about yourself, not me.

91
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:50,208
Don't be stupid.

92
00:06:50,291 --> 00:06:52,500
If anything, I'm just
getting warmed up.

93
00:06:52,583 --> 00:06:54,708
Hey, you're not ready
to bow out, are you?

94
00:06:54,791 --> 00:06:56,375
[giggles]

95
00:06:56,458 --> 00:06:57,666
Of course not.

96
00:06:57,750 --> 00:07:00,250
But when I tried
to use Fuma Korin on her,

97
00:07:00,333 --> 00:07:01,541
it didn't work.

98
00:07:01,625 --> 00:07:03,041
So now what?

99
00:07:03,125 --> 00:07:05,041
[HOMURA] It didn't work
because you tried it alone.

100
00:07:05,125 --> 00:07:07,958
-Maybe we should do it together.
-What?

101
00:07:08,041 --> 00:07:11,333
I said we're gonna use
Fuma Korin on her.

102
00:07:11,416 --> 00:07:14,250
Homura! You don't know
how to use that technique!

103
00:07:14,333 --> 00:07:16,708
[HOMURA] I've seen you do it
a bunch of times.

104
00:07:16,791 --> 00:07:19,208
So, it'll be okay.

105
00:07:19,291 --> 00:07:20,625
[ASUKA]
But you haven't practiced!

106
00:07:20,708 --> 00:07:22,083
[HOMURA]
Give me a break.

107
00:07:22,166 --> 00:07:24,833
If you can do it,
then I most certainly can too!

108
00:07:24,916 --> 00:07:26,875
Listen to me,
this move could kill you!

109
00:07:26,958 --> 00:07:29,500
Oh. Well, I'm not really worried
about that now.

110
00:07:29,583 --> 00:07:31,791
-[ASUKA] Why not?
-[HOMURA] Think about it.

111
00:07:32,875 --> 00:07:34,791
There's no way I'm gonna die.

112
00:07:36,750 --> 00:07:38,250
I'll never die.

113
00:07:38,333 --> 00:07:41,125
[BOTH] Not until I
master the path of the shinobi!

114
00:07:42,125 --> 00:07:43,416
Okay, are you ready?

115
00:07:43,500 --> 00:07:44,875
Yep! Let's do it!

116
00:07:44,958 --> 00:07:47,041
[BOTH yelling]

117
00:07:47,125 --> 00:07:49,125
[BOTH]
Hien Ranbu!

118
00:07:49,208 --> 00:07:51,500
[RASETSU grunts]

119
00:07:51,583 --> 00:07:53,333
Asuka, she's weakened!

120
00:07:53,416 --> 00:07:54,625
Right, this is our chance!

121
00:07:54,708 --> 00:07:56,500
[BOTH]
Super-Secret Ninja Art!

122
00:07:56,583 --> 00:07:59,166
Fuma Korin!

123
00:08:03,958 --> 00:08:06,916
[growling]

124
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:08,958
[yelling]

125
00:08:13,750 --> 00:08:15,625
[chuckling]

126
00:08:15,708 --> 00:08:17,291
♪

127
00:08:17,375 --> 00:08:18,541
[YUMI gasps]

128
00:08:20,250 --> 00:08:22,166
[YUMI screaming]

129
00:08:22,250 --> 00:08:26,208
♪

130
00:08:29,500 --> 00:08:31,166
[ice shatters]

131
00:08:31,250 --> 00:08:34,416
[rumbling]

132
00:08:34,500 --> 00:08:37,000
♪

133
00:08:46,791 --> 00:08:48,708
[whooshing]

134
00:08:48,791 --> 00:08:50,416
[FUBUKI]
You two again?

135
00:08:50,500 --> 00:08:51,750
What do you want?

136
00:08:52,791 --> 00:08:54,708
To save somebody.

137
00:08:54,791 --> 00:08:57,958
In that case,
I'm afraid you're too late.

138
00:08:58,041 --> 00:09:01,958
Yumi has most likely sunk to
the bottom of the lake by now.

139
00:09:02,041 --> 00:09:03,333
Well, believe it or not,

140
00:09:03,416 --> 00:09:05,500
Yumi isn't the person
who needs saving.

141
00:09:05,583 --> 00:09:08,666
[GEKKOU] The one we came
to help is in front of us.

142
00:09:08,750 --> 00:09:10,333
It's you, Lady Fubuki.

143
00:09:10,416 --> 00:09:12,500
[FUBUKI]
You help me?

144
00:09:15,958 --> 00:09:17,666
You must be joking.

145
00:09:19,458 --> 00:09:21,750
Sorry, we're not.

146
00:09:36,750 --> 00:09:37,875
[FUBUKI]
Go on then.

147
00:09:37,958 --> 00:09:39,875
Don't just stand there.

148
00:09:39,958 --> 00:09:41,916
Or perhaps I should make
the first move!

149
00:09:45,958 --> 00:09:47,291
What are you doing?

150
00:09:48,708 --> 00:09:51,875
This is a technique
that we both learned from Yumi.

151
00:09:51,958 --> 00:09:55,458
It's the justice
that Master Kurokage taught her.

152
00:09:55,541 --> 00:09:56,875
She called it warmth.

153
00:09:56,958 --> 00:09:58,875
Unhand me!

154
00:10:00,041 --> 00:10:01,666
I had warmth, but who was it

155
00:10:01,750 --> 00:10:03,458
that ripped
everything away from me?

156
00:10:03,541 --> 00:10:05,791
It was the shinobi!

157
00:10:05,875 --> 00:10:09,083
But if you want,
you can have that warmth again!

158
00:10:09,166 --> 00:10:12,125
[GEKKOU] That's right,
because we still care about you!

159
00:10:12,208 --> 00:10:14,208
I have the blood of a youma!

160
00:10:14,291 --> 00:10:17,958
Human warmth can't reach me,
and it'll never be able to!

161
00:10:18,041 --> 00:10:19,250
[GIRLS gasping]

162
00:10:19,333 --> 00:10:22,875
Let go!
If you don't, you'll die!

163
00:10:22,958 --> 00:10:24,875
No, we won't abandon you!

164
00:10:24,958 --> 00:10:28,208
Not now, or ever!
We'll always be here!

165
00:10:28,291 --> 00:10:29,625
[GIRLS screaming]

166
00:10:29,708 --> 00:10:31,166
[GROUP grunts]

167
00:10:32,875 --> 00:10:34,166
[FUBUKI]
What are you doing here?

168
00:10:37,458 --> 00:10:38,875
You're all too late.

169
00:10:38,958 --> 00:10:40,916
Yumi's dead.

170
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:41,875
I killed her.

171
00:10:41,958 --> 00:10:43,833
[GIRLS gasp]

172
00:10:43,916 --> 00:10:48,375
♪

173
00:10:48,458 --> 00:10:50,958
[wind whistling]

174
00:10:54,125 --> 00:10:55,458
[BOTH chuckle]

175
00:10:56,958 --> 00:10:58,708
[FUBUKI]
Have you given up on fighting?

176
00:10:58,791 --> 00:11:00,208
[YOZAKURA]
No.

177
00:11:00,291 --> 00:11:02,666
There's no point in begging
for your life, you know.

178
00:11:02,750 --> 00:11:05,666
We won't be fighting you.
That's someone else's job.

179
00:11:05,750 --> 00:11:07,083
-Yep!
-Right.

180
00:11:07,166 --> 00:11:09,541
In the end,
it's totally gotta be Yumi.

181
00:11:09,625 --> 00:11:12,875
Are you all deaf
or did I not make myself clear?

182
00:11:12,958 --> 00:11:14,500
I told you that she's dead.

183
00:11:18,125 --> 00:11:20,625
[ALL chuckle]

184
00:11:23,666 --> 00:11:25,083
Impossible.

185
00:11:28,750 --> 00:11:30,791
♪

186
00:11:30,875 --> 00:11:32,541
[gasps]

187
00:11:32,625 --> 00:11:36,083
[roars]

188
00:11:36,166 --> 00:11:38,583
[ASUKA]
No. We can't seal her.

189
00:11:38,666 --> 00:11:39,625
Damn it.

190
00:11:39,708 --> 00:11:41,583
[MIYABI]
Wow, this is pathetic.

191
00:11:42,666 --> 00:11:43,833
[ASUKA]
Miyabi?

192
00:11:43,916 --> 00:11:48,000
♪

193
00:11:48,083 --> 00:11:49,625
[MIYABI yells]

194
00:11:50,750 --> 00:11:53,875
I told you, my goal is
to become the ultimate shinobi!

195
00:11:55,166 --> 00:11:56,875
What are you doing?

196
00:11:56,958 --> 00:11:59,250
[MIYABI] But I still have
a long way to go.

197
00:11:59,333 --> 00:12:02,625
Because I almost forgot what
I learned when I lost my mother.

198
00:12:04,416 --> 00:12:06,208
-She can't be.
-But she is!

199
00:12:06,291 --> 00:12:08,833
When you fight for
the sole purpose of revenge,

200
00:12:08,916 --> 00:12:10,875
you'll never attain
true strength.

201
00:12:10,958 --> 00:12:11,916
And so...

202
00:12:13,250 --> 00:12:14,708
Fuma Korin!

203
00:12:14,791 --> 00:12:17,416
[yells]

204
00:12:17,500 --> 00:12:23,000
[roaring]

205
00:12:23,083 --> 00:12:26,500
[gasping]

206
00:12:26,583 --> 00:12:29,083
♪

207
00:12:30,458 --> 00:12:31,541
[gasps]

208
00:12:33,458 --> 00:12:36,541
I have no regrets,
because in the end,

209
00:12:36,625 --> 00:12:40,416
I fought for Fubuki,
and that's all that matters.

210
00:12:42,000 --> 00:12:44,166
Rasetsu, I'm sorry!

211
00:12:47,708 --> 00:12:50,291
♪

212
00:12:53,333 --> 00:12:54,875
-[RASETSU] Fubuki...
-[FUBUKI gasps]

213
00:12:54,958 --> 00:12:58,416
♪

214
00:12:58,500 --> 00:13:01,083
I see, Rasetsu.

215
00:13:01,166 --> 00:13:03,500
♪

216
00:13:07,291 --> 00:13:08,875
[grunts]

217
00:13:08,958 --> 00:13:10,666
Yumi!

218
00:13:10,750 --> 00:13:11,958
[YUMI]
Let's go!

219
00:13:14,916 --> 00:13:16,458
Why won't you die?

220
00:13:18,625 --> 00:13:21,291
No matter what,
I'll keep on fighting!

221
00:13:21,375 --> 00:13:23,916
Whatever it takes for you
to understand my power!

222
00:13:24,000 --> 00:13:25,833
I... No.

223
00:13:25,916 --> 00:13:27,208
You and I...

224
00:13:28,416 --> 00:13:30,500
we have to work together
to end this war

225
00:13:30,583 --> 00:13:32,416
between shinobi and youma!

226
00:13:32,500 --> 00:13:36,166
Being an unyielding shield isn't
going to help either of us.

227
00:13:36,250 --> 00:13:39,750
But a sword filled with warmth
can save everyone!

228
00:13:40,958 --> 00:13:42,208
That is my justice!

229
00:13:42,291 --> 00:13:44,125
The justice...

230
00:13:45,541 --> 00:13:46,708
of the moon!

231
00:13:46,791 --> 00:13:48,500
♪

232
00:13:48,583 --> 00:13:49,708
[FUBUKI gasps]

233
00:13:49,791 --> 00:13:51,333
[FUBUKI screams]

234
00:13:51,416 --> 00:13:53,916
[wind whooshing]

235
00:13:54,958 --> 00:13:56,291
[grunting]

236
00:13:59,541 --> 00:14:02,958
[groaning]

237
00:14:03,041 --> 00:14:05,000
[breathing heavily]

238
00:14:10,958 --> 00:14:15,000
[YOUMA growling]

239
00:14:20,208 --> 00:14:23,041
-Take this!
-[YOUMA screeching]

240
00:14:24,708 --> 00:14:26,458
Excellent work, as usual.

241
00:14:26,541 --> 00:14:29,125
Well, annihilating youma
is the reason I exist.

242
00:14:29,208 --> 00:14:30,625
It's my purpose.

243
00:14:30,708 --> 00:14:32,208
For all of eternity.

244
00:14:33,208 --> 00:14:35,916
[SHINOBI talking indistinctly]

245
00:14:40,000 --> 00:14:41,625
Yes, I understand.

246
00:14:41,708 --> 00:14:44,291
I'll be sure to tell
everyone else.

247
00:14:44,375 --> 00:14:46,333
So, what's going on?

248
00:14:46,416 --> 00:14:48,041
Who were you talking to?

249
00:14:48,125 --> 00:14:50,000
Oh, it's Suzune-Sensei.

250
00:14:50,083 --> 00:14:52,458
She said they've just
finished up at the Kikai Dome.

251
00:14:52,541 --> 00:14:54,041
That's wonderful!

252
00:14:54,125 --> 00:14:56,458
Yes, and everyone is safe.

253
00:14:56,541 --> 00:14:57,833
Kiriya-Sensei, too?

254
00:14:57,916 --> 00:14:59,375
[HARUKA]
Of course!

255
00:14:59,458 --> 00:15:01,125
And Master Hanzou and Sayuri

256
00:15:01,208 --> 00:15:03,125
have already sealed away
all the youma.

257
00:15:03,208 --> 00:15:04,541
[HOMURA grunts]

258
00:15:04,625 --> 00:15:05,916
♪

259
00:15:06,000 --> 00:15:08,125
-[MIYABI grunts]
-[ASUKA laughs]

260
00:15:08,208 --> 00:15:10,583
♪

261
00:15:14,208 --> 00:15:16,083
♪

262
00:15:18,291 --> 00:15:21,250
[wind gusting]

263
00:15:22,750 --> 00:15:26,250
[footsteps approaching]

264
00:15:45,708 --> 00:15:47,041
You dropped this earlier.

265
00:15:50,833 --> 00:15:52,708
All right, who's ready
to head home?

266
00:15:52,791 --> 00:15:54,000
-Oh, I am!
-[YUMI] Let's go.

267
00:15:54,083 --> 00:15:55,750
Yeah, it's freezing here.

268
00:15:55,833 --> 00:15:57,166
[SHIKI]
I want a hot bath.

269
00:15:57,250 --> 00:15:58,541
[MINORI]
Me, too!

270
00:16:08,583 --> 00:16:10,208
♪

271
00:16:13,291 --> 00:16:16,125
Hey, we could use more ornaments
on this side of the tree.

272
00:16:16,208 --> 00:16:18,291
No problem,
just leave it to me!

273
00:16:18,375 --> 00:16:20,916
Here. Give me some
and I can help, too.

274
00:16:21,000 --> 00:16:22,958
I just spoke to Asuka,

275
00:16:23,041 --> 00:16:25,083
and she said that she and Yumi
will be here soon.

276
00:16:25,166 --> 00:16:27,916
Excuse me.

277
00:16:28,000 --> 00:16:29,541
Why do I have to wear this?

278
00:16:29,625 --> 00:16:32,250
The entire outfit seems
really impractical.

279
00:16:32,333 --> 00:16:33,583
But...

280
00:16:33,666 --> 00:16:35,500
you can't have Christmas
without a reindeer.

281
00:16:35,583 --> 00:16:38,500
That doesn't explain
the squid outfit.

282
00:16:38,583 --> 00:16:40,500
♪

283
00:16:40,583 --> 00:16:45,041
[grunting]

284
00:16:46,958 --> 00:16:49,000
She's so amazing.

285
00:16:49,083 --> 00:16:50,708
Yeah. Just look at the way

286
00:16:50,791 --> 00:16:52,791
the sweat is dripping
from her body.

287
00:16:52,875 --> 00:16:55,333
This sucks.
It's Christmas day, after all!

288
00:16:55,416 --> 00:16:57,166
Why do we have to sit here
and train?

289
00:16:57,250 --> 00:16:58,791
Don't be sad, Ryobi.

290
00:16:58,875 --> 00:17:00,625
Think of it
as a new kinky technique,

291
00:17:00,708 --> 00:17:04,000
AKA a tech-kink, it'll make
your whole body go jingle bells!

292
00:17:04,083 --> 00:17:05,541
See?

293
00:17:05,625 --> 00:17:08,041
Jingle. Bells!

294
00:17:08,125 --> 00:17:10,541
I'm feeling extra jingly!

295
00:17:10,625 --> 00:17:12,416
[RYOBI]
That doesn't even make sense,

296
00:17:12,500 --> 00:17:13,833
-you stupid dog!
-[RYONA screams]

297
00:17:13,916 --> 00:17:15,416
[MIYABI]
I can't afford to rest.

298
00:17:15,500 --> 00:17:18,583
No matter what, I have to become
the ultimate shinobi!

299
00:17:19,875 --> 00:17:21,041
[RENKA]
Check it out!

300
00:17:21,125 --> 00:17:23,625
Our giant snowman
is finally finished!

301
00:17:23,708 --> 00:17:26,208
Whatevs. That thing
was like a ton of work.

302
00:17:26,291 --> 00:17:28,791
Hold up. It feels like
it's missing something.

303
00:17:28,875 --> 00:17:30,625
It needs some decorations!

304
00:17:30,708 --> 00:17:32,333
Yeah, since it's Christmas!

305
00:17:33,333 --> 00:17:34,958
Now it's the bomb!

306
00:17:35,041 --> 00:17:36,541
[KAFURU]
But those are fireworks.

307
00:17:36,625 --> 00:17:38,208
Don't bombs explode?

308
00:17:38,291 --> 00:17:39,625
They sure do!

309
00:17:39,708 --> 00:17:40,916
[laughter]

310
00:17:41,000 --> 00:17:42,750
[KAFURU]
You're gonna get us killed.

311
00:17:42,833 --> 00:17:45,333
-What's with all that noise?
-[KAGURA chuckles]

312
00:17:45,416 --> 00:17:48,666
It's fine.
Just a Christmas celebration.

313
00:17:48,750 --> 00:17:50,375
♪

314
00:17:50,458 --> 00:17:53,458
[HARUKA sighs] I can't believe
we're working on Christmas.

315
00:17:53,541 --> 00:17:55,125
[HOMURA]
Well, we were so busy fighting

316
00:17:55,208 --> 00:17:57,083
we weren't able
to pick up any shifts.

317
00:17:57,166 --> 00:17:59,625
[MIRAI] That's true,
but it's not like working today

318
00:17:59,708 --> 00:18:02,000
is going to earn us
any turkeys or a cake.

319
00:18:02,083 --> 00:18:03,166
That's a good point.

320
00:18:03,250 --> 00:18:04,875
Cheer up, guys,
I can always make us

321
00:18:04,958 --> 00:18:07,208
a bean sprout cake
for Christmas, 'kay?

322
00:18:07,291 --> 00:18:08,458
It's okay, ladies,

323
00:18:08,541 --> 00:18:10,083
-there's no need to worry.
-[YOMI] Huh?

324
00:18:10,166 --> 00:18:13,541
I spoke to the manager,
and he said if we work hard,

325
00:18:13,625 --> 00:18:15,708
that he'll just give us
whatever cakes and turkey

326
00:18:15,791 --> 00:18:17,458
they have left over for free!

327
00:18:17,541 --> 00:18:18,958
[GIRLS gasp]

328
00:18:19,041 --> 00:18:20,791
Okay, let's get to it!

329
00:18:20,875 --> 00:18:22,625
Because when the five of us
work together,

330
00:18:22,708 --> 00:18:24,208
there's nothing we can't do!

331
00:18:24,291 --> 00:18:25,500
[ALL]
Yeah!

332
00:18:30,125 --> 00:18:31,708
[YUMI]
Hey, Asuka.

333
00:18:31,791 --> 00:18:33,000
How've you been feeling lately?

334
00:18:33,083 --> 00:18:34,125
Oh.

335
00:18:34,208 --> 00:18:35,500
I'm just fine now,

336
00:18:35,583 --> 00:18:37,583
and I'm even back
to training with everyone.

337
00:18:37,666 --> 00:18:40,250
Plus the marks have
completely disappeared.

338
00:18:40,333 --> 00:18:41,875
Are you sure?

339
00:18:41,958 --> 00:18:43,791
You still shouldn't
push yourself too hard.

340
00:18:43,875 --> 00:18:45,333
Honestly, I'm good.

341
00:18:45,416 --> 00:18:46,583
The only thing I want right now

342
00:18:46,666 --> 00:18:48,500
is to enjoy the holidays
with everybody.

343
00:18:48,583 --> 00:18:50,541
We worked so hard to get here.

344
00:18:51,583 --> 00:18:52,625
True, let's have fun.

345
00:18:52,708 --> 00:18:54,458
Oh, I'm planning on it!

346
00:18:54,541 --> 00:18:55,791
I can't wait.

347
00:19:01,791 --> 00:19:02,916
It's Fubuki.

348
00:19:09,375 --> 00:19:11,916
I'm not going to kill
any more youma.

349
00:19:12,000 --> 00:19:15,250
As a shinobi, I'll risk my life
to seal them away.

350
00:19:15,333 --> 00:19:17,208
No matter what anyone tells me,

351
00:19:17,291 --> 00:19:19,166
I've made up my mind.

352
00:19:19,250 --> 00:19:21,458
That is my plan as well.

353
00:19:23,958 --> 00:19:27,583
You know, if everything
in this world has a counterpart,

354
00:19:27,666 --> 00:19:30,000
then the shinobi
and youma are a pair.

355
00:19:30,083 --> 00:19:33,250
Perhaps one day,
you and I will face off again.

356
00:19:33,333 --> 00:19:35,208
Who knows what the future holds?

357
00:19:37,750 --> 00:19:38,958
[YUMI gasps]

358
00:19:46,333 --> 00:19:48,000
[FUBUKI]
I want you to have it.

359
00:19:48,083 --> 00:19:48,916
Are you sure?

360
00:19:49,000 --> 00:19:50,583
Yes, I don't need it.

361
00:19:50,666 --> 00:19:52,458
Not like I once did.

362
00:19:55,458 --> 00:19:57,125
[YUMI]
I'll cherish it.

363
00:19:57,208 --> 00:19:58,666
[FUBUKI]
Farewell.

364
00:19:58,750 --> 00:20:01,958
I'm off to try and find my place
in this human world.

365
00:20:05,083 --> 00:20:06,291
Hey!

366
00:20:08,208 --> 00:20:11,958
Fubuki, I never had
the opportunity to fight you.

367
00:20:12,041 --> 00:20:14,500
One day, let's continue
the Shinobi Masters.

368
00:20:15,625 --> 00:20:17,458
[chuckles]

369
00:20:17,541 --> 00:20:20,416
♪

370
00:20:31,708 --> 00:20:34,500
You two.
Why are you still following me?

371
00:20:36,500 --> 00:20:38,500
Aren't you ever lonely
by yourself?

372
00:20:38,583 --> 00:20:41,333
[FUBUKI]
No, because I'm not alone.

373
00:20:41,416 --> 00:20:43,375
Somewhere, in another place,

374
00:20:43,458 --> 00:20:45,500
my mother and Rasetsu
are with me.

375
00:20:45,583 --> 00:20:47,583
And you have me
and Gekkou as well.

376
00:20:47,666 --> 00:20:48,916
That's right.

377
00:20:49,000 --> 00:20:53,875
♪

378
00:20:53,958 --> 00:20:55,375
It certainly is.

379
00:20:55,458 --> 00:20:59,958
♪

380
00:21:00,041 --> 00:21:01,250
Take this.

381
00:21:03,041 --> 00:21:05,125
I want you to have the sword.

382
00:21:05,208 --> 00:21:07,708
And I'll keep the shield
with me, okay?

383
00:21:07,791 --> 00:21:08,958
Sounds good.

384
00:21:10,083 --> 00:21:11,125
Thanks, Yumi!

385
00:21:11,208 --> 00:21:13,125
♪

386
00:21:13,208 --> 00:21:14,666
That reminds me.

387
00:21:14,750 --> 00:21:17,125
There's a question
I've always wanted to ask you.

388
00:21:17,208 --> 00:21:19,041
Okay, what is it?

389
00:21:19,125 --> 00:21:22,208
I've always wondered what kind
of shinobi you want to be.

390
00:21:22,291 --> 00:21:23,541
That's a good question.

391
00:21:23,625 --> 00:21:25,833
♪

392
00:21:29,458 --> 00:21:30,583
I suppose...

393
00:21:32,666 --> 00:21:36,250
I want to be the kind of shinobi
that's like this falling snow.

394
00:21:36,333 --> 00:21:37,625
[ASUKA gasps]

395
00:21:38,666 --> 00:21:41,083
It covers the world
like a blanket

396
00:21:41,166 --> 00:21:42,541
until it's warm again,

397
00:21:42,625 --> 00:21:44,208
and then it melts
and disappears.

398
00:21:46,083 --> 00:21:49,666
A shinobi like the snow.
That's me.

399
00:21:49,750 --> 00:21:52,166
♪

400
00:21:52,250 --> 00:21:54,625
Even when it melts,
the memory remains.

401
00:21:54,708 --> 00:21:57,208
You're right.
That makes sense.

402
00:21:57,291 --> 00:21:58,583
[BOTH laugh]

403
00:21:58,666 --> 00:22:00,416
Come on, we should hurry.

404
00:22:00,500 --> 00:22:02,208
Where there is light,
there is darkness.

405
00:22:02,291 --> 00:22:03,791
Okay!

406
00:22:03,875 --> 00:22:06,208
[ASUKA] This is the story
of a select group of girls.

407
00:22:06,291 --> 00:22:09,250
♪

408
00:22:09,333 --> 00:22:10,791
[YUMI/ASUKA]
They are the shinobi warriors

409
00:22:10,875 --> 00:22:12,666
who live in the shadows.

